label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性脑脊髓炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":51,"end":55,"text":"共济失调","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":56,"end":60,"text":"快速震颤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":67,"text":"头部震颤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":65,"text":"头部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":65,"end":67,"text":"震颤","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 鸡传染性脑脊髓炎(Avian Encephalomyelitis，AE)是一种主要侵害幼鸡的传染病，以共济失调和快速震颤特别是头部震颤为特征。AE很大程度上是一种经蛋传播的疾病。

label: [{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"小鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"小鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 临床症状：经垂直传播而感染的小鸡潜伏期1～7天，经水平传播感染的小鸡，其潜伏期为11天以上(12～30天)。

label: [{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"石岐杂鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":15,"text":"3周龄以内的雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 此病主要发生于3周龄以内的雏鸡，笔者也曾多次确诊过于6～7周龄的石岐杂鸡发生AE的病例。

label: [{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"病雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"迟钝","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":36,"end":50,"text":"小鸡不愿走动或走几步就蹲下来","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":51,"end":58,"text":"常以跗关节着地","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":63,"end":67,"text":"共济失调","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":68,"end":72,"text":"走路蹒跚","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":73,"end":77,"text":"步态不稳","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":78,"end":94,"text":"驱赶时勉强用跗关节走路并拍动翅膀","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"小鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":53,"end":56,"text":"跗关节","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":84,"end":87,"text":"跗关节","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":92,"end":94,"text":"翅膀","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 在自然暴发的病例中，雏鸡出壳后就陆续发病，病雏最初表现为迟钝，精神沉郁，小鸡不愿走动或走几步就蹲下来，常以跗关节着地，继而出现共济失调，走路蹒跚，步态不稳，驱赶时勉强用跗关节走路并拍动翅膀。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"倒地侧卧","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":41,"end":50,"text":"阵发性音叉式的震颤","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":25,"text":"头颈部震颤","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"震颤","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"头颈部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病雏一般在发病3天后出现麻痹而倒地侧卧，头颈部震颤一般在发病5天后逐渐出现，一般呈阵发性音叉式的震颤；人工刺激如给水加料、驱赶、倒提时可激发。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"运动障碍","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"羽毛不整","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"发育受阻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":37,"text":"平均体重明显低于正常水平","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":43,"text":"存活鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":45,"end":64,"text":"一侧或两侧眼球的晶状体混浊或浅蓝色褪色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":65,"end":72,"text":"眼球增大及失明","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":59,"end":62,"text":"浅蓝色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"褪色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":67,"end":69,"text":"增大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":70,"end":72,"text":"失明","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":50,"end":52,"text":"眼球","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":53,"end":56,"text":"晶状体","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":65,"end":67,"text":"眼球","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":9,"text":"趾关节卷曲","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"卷曲","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"趾关节","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有些病鸡趾关节卷曲、运动障碍、羽毛不整和发育受阻，平均体重明显低于正常水平。部分存活鸡可见一侧或两侧眼球的晶状体混浊或浅蓝色褪色，眼球增大及失明。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"小鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"运动障碍","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":36,"text":"饥渴衰竭死亡","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 发病早期小鸡食欲尚好，但因运动障碍，病鸡难以接近食槽和水槽而饥渴衰竭死亡。

label: [{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":25,"text":"细菌性感染","labels":["disease"]},{"start":37,"end":44,"text":"血清学阳性反应","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"中成鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 在大群饲养条件下，鸡只也会互相践踏或继发细菌性感染而死亡。中成鸡感染除出现血清学阳性反应外，无明显的临诊症状及肉眼可见的病理变化。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":46,"end":50,"text":"蛋重减少","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":38,"text":"孵化率可下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":52,"end":57,"text":"畸形蛋稍多","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":59,"end":67,"text":"蛋壳颜色基本正常","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 产蛋鸡感染后产蛋下降16%～43%。产蛋下降后1～2周恢复正常。孵化率可下降10%～35%，蛋重减少，除畸形蛋稍多外，蛋壳颜色基本正常。

label: [{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"内脏器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":60,"text":"病雏肌胃的肌层有散在的灰白区","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"病雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"肌胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"肌层","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":61,"end":64,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":34,"text":"脑膜血管充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"脑膜血管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 剖检变化：一般内脏器官无特征性的肉眼病变，个别病例能见到脑膜血管充血、出血。如细心观察可偶见病雏肌胃的肌层有散在的灰白区。成年鸡发病无上述病变。

label: [{"start":13,"end":19,"text":"中枢神经系统","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"内脏器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"肌胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"胰腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"心肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"组织学病变","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 组织学病变：主要病变集中在中枢神经系统和部分内脏器官如肌胃、腺胃、胰腺、心肌和肾脏等，而周围神经无病变，这是一个重要的鉴别诊断要点。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"中枢神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"病毒性脑炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":23,"text":"神经元变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":30,"text":"胶质细胞增生","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"血管套","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"增生","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"变性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"神经元","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"胶质细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"血管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 中枢神经主要显示病毒性脑炎的病变，如神经元变性，胶质细胞增生和血管套现象。

label: [{"start":17,"end":29,"text":"可见神经元中央染色质溶解","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"溶解","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":37,"text":"神经元细胞肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":45,"text":"树突和轴突消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":54,"text":"细胞核偏移或消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"偏移","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":75,"text":"仅剩下染色均匀的粉红色或紫红色神经元残迹","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":66,"text":"粉红色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":67,"end":70,"text":"紫红色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":27,"text":"神经元中央染色质","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":35,"text":"神经元细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"腰脊髓","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":1,"end":3,"text":"延脑","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"脊髓","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"灰质","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"树突","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"轴突","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":46,"end":49,"text":"细胞核","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":70,"end":73,"text":"神经元","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 在延脑和脊髓(特别是腰脊髓)灰质中可见神经元中央染色质溶解、神经元细胞肿大、树突和轴突消失、细胞核偏移或消失，仅剩下染色均匀的粉红色或紫红色神经元残迹。

label: [{"start":11,"end":27,"text":"延脑和脊髓中发现有胶质细胞增生灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"增生灶","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":49,"text":"脑组织内有以淋巴细胞性管层为主的血管套现象","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":1,"end":3,"text":"中脑","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":10,"text":"小脑的分子层","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"延脑","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"脊髓","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"胶质细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":31,"text":"脑组织","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":41,"text":"淋巴细胞性管层","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":44,"end":47,"text":"血管套","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"血管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 在中脑、小脑的分子层、延脑和脊髓中发现有胶质细胞增生灶。脑组织内有以淋巴细胞性管层为主的血管套现象。

label: [{"start":10,"end":18,"text":"淋巴细胞灶性增生","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"增生","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"内脏器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"淋巴细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"腺胃粘膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"肌层","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"胰腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"肌胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":35,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 内脏器官的病变表现为淋巴细胞灶性增生，在腺胃粘膜和肌层、胰腺、肌胃、肾等器官切片中均有发现。

label: [{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"脑","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":15,"end":20,"text":"鸡胚卵黄囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 1日龄脑内接种发病的鸡及6日龄鸡胚卵黄囊接种后孵出的病鸡，其相应器官的组织切片均不同程度地发现上述的病理学变化。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"脚弱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"瘫痪","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 1、与有脚弱、瘫痪等症状的疾病区别。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":11,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"拉绿粪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"头颈扭曲","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":28,"end":37,"text":"腺胃及消化道有出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":46,"text":"HI抗体明显增高","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":57,"text":"病毒性脑炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":75,"end":87,"text":"组织学无淋巴细胞灶性增生","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":85,"end":87,"text":"增生","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"存活鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":95,"end":96,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":15,"text":"粪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"绿","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":21,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":22,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":42,"text":"HI抗体","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":65,"end":67,"text":"肌胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":68,"end":70,"text":"胰腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":71,"end":75,"text":"内脏器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":79,"end":83,"text":"淋巴细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":97,"end":100,"text":"红细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"扭曲","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 鸡新城疫：有呼吸道症状，拉绿粪，存活鸡有头颈扭曲的症状，腺胃及消化道有出血。HI抗体明显增高，组织学虽有病毒性脑炎的病变，但腺胃、肌胃、胰腺等内脏器官组织学无淋巴细胞灶性增生，分离病毒能凝集鸡的红细胞。

label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":30,"text":"内脏肿瘤病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":37,"text":"外周神经病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":39,"end":49,"text":"单侧性的坐骨神经肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":59,"text":"外周神经系统","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"外周神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":43,"end":47,"text":"坐骨神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"内脏肿瘤","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 马立克氏病：临诊死亡一般发生在70日龄以后，而有内脏肿瘤病变和外周神经病变，如单侧性的坐骨神经肿大。AE无外周神经系统的病变。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"病毒性关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":19,"end":20,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"跛行","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"跗关节肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"发育迟缓","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":46,"end":50,"text":"嘴脚苍白","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":51,"end":57,"text":"羽毛生长不良","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":59,"end":71,"text":"心肌纤维间有异噬细胞浸润","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"浸润","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":38,"end":39,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"跗关节","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":47,"end":48,"text":"脚","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":46,"end":47,"text":"嘴","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":59,"end":63,"text":"心肌纤维","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":65,"end":69,"text":"异噬细胞","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"苍白","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":53,"end":57,"text":"生长不良","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 病毒性关节炎：自然感染多发于4～7周龄鸡，病鸡跛行，跗关节肿胀，鸡群中有部分鸡呈现发育迟缓、嘴脚苍白、羽毛生长不良等，心肌纤维间有异噬细胞浸润。

label: [{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"葡萄球菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"大肠杆菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"关节炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"关节","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":33,"text":"红肿热疼","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 其他细菌感染如葡萄球菌、大肠杆菌等引起的关节炎可引起关节的红肿热疼等炎症症状。

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"硒缺乏","labels":["disease"]},{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"硒","labels":["drug"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"维生素E","labels":["drug"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"脑软化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"小脑充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"脑回不清","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":49,"text":"局部缺血性坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"脑","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"小脑","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"脑回","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":50,"end":53,"text":"脱髓鞘","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"髓鞘","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"软化","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 维生素E、硒缺乏：肉眼可见脑软化，小脑充血、出血、肿胀和脑回不清等病变，组织学病变如局部缺血性坏死，脱髓鞘等。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"硒缺乏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":17,"text":"腹部皮下有多量液体积聚","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"蓝紫色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":45,"text":"胸肌有白线状坏死的肌纤维","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":46,"end":52,"text":"补充维生素E","labels":["control"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"维生素E","labels":["drug"]},{"start":53,"end":56,"text":"硒合剂","labels":["drug"]},{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"腹部皮下","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"胸肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"肌纤维","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"肌肉苍白","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"苍白","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 硒缺乏病可见腹部皮下有多量液体积聚，有时呈蓝紫色，有些鸡肌肉苍白，胸肌有白线状坏死的肌纤维。补充维生素E、硒合剂能控制病情。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"维生素B2缺乏","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":17,"text":"2周龄雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":26,"text":"脚趾向内弯曲","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"腿麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"行走困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"向内弯曲","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":49,"text":"坐骨神经比正常肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"脚趾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"坐骨神经","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 维生素B2缺乏：常发生于2周龄雏鸡。雏鸡脚趾向内弯曲，腿麻痹，行走困难，剖检时见坐骨神经比正常肿大3～4倍。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"幼雏维生素B2缺乏","labels":["disease"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"幼雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"种鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"B2缺乏","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":34,"text":"喂服维生素B2","labels":["control"]},{"start":29,"end":34,"text":"维生素B2","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 幼雏维生素B2缺乏是由种鸡群B2缺乏引起的，每只鸡每天喂服维生素B25mg可得到改善。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"维生素B1缺乏","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"烟酸缺乏","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":20,"text":"维生素D3缺乏","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"脚弱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"脚","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 维生素B1缺乏、烟酸缺乏、维生素D3缺乏也会引起脚弱症状，适当地补充能控制病情，改善症状。

label: [{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"药物中毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":20,"text":"抗球虫药拉沙星菌素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":28,"end":31,"text":"氯霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"莫能霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":39,"end":42,"text":"盐霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":43,"end":46,"text":"红霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":47,"end":50,"text":"氯霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":51,"end":54,"text":"枝原净","labels":["drug"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":64,"end":66,"text":"脚软","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":67,"end":71,"text":"共济失调","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":64,"end":65,"text":"脚","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 中毒性因素：药物中毒如抗球虫药拉沙星菌素使用时间过长或与氯霉素合用；莫能霉素或盐霉素与红霉素、氯霉素、枝原净等同时使用，会使雏鸡脚软，共济失调等。

label: [{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"氟中毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"磷酸氢钙","labels":["drug"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"腿无力","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"走路不稳","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"跛行","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"瘫痪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":50,"end":60,"text":"鸡胸骨发育与日龄不符","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":61,"end":65,"text":"腿骨松软","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":66,"end":71,"text":"易折而不断","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"胸骨","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"腿骨","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":50,"end":51,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":63,"end":65,"text":"松软","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"无力","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 另外近年来因使用含氟过高的磷酸氢钙而造成的氟中毒，雏鸡腿无力，走路不稳，严重时出现跛行或瘫痪，剖检见鸡胸骨发育与日龄不符，腿骨松软，易折而不断。

label: [{"start":25,"end":29,"text":"血钙降低","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":24,"text":"不溶性氧化物","labels":["disease"]},{"start":53,"end":57,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"血钙","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"血钙","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"血钙","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"骨钙","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":45,"end":50,"text":"骨钙化不全","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 主要原因是高氟进入机体后与血钙结合成不溶性氧化物使血钙降低，为补充血钙，骨钙不断释放而导致骨钙化不全。引起产蛋下降

label: [{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 2、与引起产蛋下降，但无明显的症状和不引起鸡死亡的疾病的区别。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"产蛋下降综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":14,"text":"产蛋严重下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":20,"text":"持续时间长","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":34,"text":"恢复后产蛋很难达到原来水平","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":36,"end":41,"text":"蛋壳变白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":42,"end":46,"text":"产无壳蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":54,"text":"软壳蛋或畸形蛋","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 产蛋下降综合征：产蛋严重下降，持续时间长，恢复后产蛋很难达到原来水平，且蛋壳变白色，产无壳蛋、软壳蛋或畸形蛋。

label: [{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"腺病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":9,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"鸡血细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 减蛋后1周取输卵管的刮落物作病料接种鸭胚，可分离到能凝集鸡血细胞的腺病毒。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":14,"text":"呼吸性症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":25,"text":"畸形蛋增加","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"蛋的品质变化","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":39,"text":"蛋清稀薄如水","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 传染性支气管炎：有呼吸性症状，产蛋下降，畸形蛋增加，蛋的品质变化，蛋清稀薄如水。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"非典型新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":15,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 非典型新城疫：只有产蛋下降，鸡无明显的症状，减蛋1周后，HI抗体明显上升。

label: [{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":0,"end":12,"text":"低致病力毒株引起的禽流感","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 低致病力毒株引起的禽流感：只有产蛋下降，通过血清学及病原分离进行鉴别。

label: [{"start":2,"end":11,"text":"加强消毒与隔离措施","labels":["control"]}]
text: 1．加强消毒与隔离措施，防止从疫区引进种苗和种蛋。

label: [{"start":2,"end":3,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 2．鸡感染后一个月内的蛋不宜孵化。

label: [{"start":17,"end":24,"text":"轻症鸡隔离饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"轻症鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"隔离饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":25,"end":41,"text":"加强管理并投与抗生素预防细菌感染","labels":["control"]},{"start":37,"end":41,"text":"细菌感染","labels":["disease"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"抗生素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":42,"end":46,"text":"维生素E","labels":["drug"]},{"start":47,"end":52,"text":"维生素B1","labels":["drug"]},{"start":53,"end":56,"text":"谷维素","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 3．AE发生后，尚无特异性疗法。将轻症鸡隔离饲养，加强管理并投与抗生素预防细菌感染，维生素E、维生素B1、谷维素等药可保护神经和改善症状。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"重症鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"卵黄抗体","labels":["drug"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"康复鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":47,"end":51,"text":"肌肉注射","labels":["control"]},{"start":54,"end":56,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 重症鸡应挑出淘汰。全群还可用抗AE的卵黄抗体(康复鸡或免疫后抗体滴度较高的鸡群所产的蛋制成)作肌肉注射，每只雏鸡0.5～1.0ml，每日1次，连用2天。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"雏鸡传染性脑脊髓炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":20,"text":"滤过性病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":34,"text":"神经系统","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":45,"text":"地方流行性传染病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 雏鸡传染性脑脊髓炎：本病是一种滤过性病毒引起的、主要侵害雏鸡神经系统的一种地方流行性传染病。

label: [{"start":11,"end":16,"text":"冬春季多发","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"流行病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: (一)流行病学特征：以冬春季多发，1～2日龄雏鸡易感，7～14日龄雏鸡最易感。

label: [{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"种鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 其传播途径，一是经卵传播，种鸡带毒，所产种蛋也带毒，孵出的雏鸡先天性感染本病毒而发病；

label: [{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":60,"end":62,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":52,"text":"消化道感染","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":63,"end":72,"text":"发病率与死亡率较高","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":50,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 二是水平传播，雏鸡患病后由粪便排毒，污染环境，被污染的饲料、饮水、用具、人员等成为传递因素，经消化道感染。本病传播迅速，雏鸡的发病率与死亡率较高，一旦发病，损失严重。

label: [{"start":16,"end":22,"text":"神经系统紊乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"神经系统","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"紊乱","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: (二)临床症状：本病的主要表现是神经系统紊乱。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"病雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"共济失调","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":28,"text":"前后倾斜左右晃动","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"跌倒","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"伏卧","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"侧卧","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":39,"end":49,"text":"跗关节着地呈蹲伏姿势","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":52,"end":56,"text":"反应迟钝","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":57,"end":61,"text":"全身颤抖","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":62,"end":66,"text":"转圈运动","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":67,"end":71,"text":"头颈扭转","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":39,"end":42,"text":"跗关节","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":67,"end":68,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":68,"end":69,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"扭转","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 初期，见病雏精神沉郁；随后出现共济失调，前后倾斜左右晃动，跌倒，伏卧或侧卧，或跗关节着地呈蹲伏姿势；进而反应迟钝，全身颤抖，转圈运动或头颈扭转。

label: [{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":36,"text":"产蛋率暂时性下降","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 水平感染时，症状多不明显，常被人忽略。成年鸡感染时，只有产蛋率暂时性下降，耐过之后，产蛋率逐渐恢复。

label: [{"start":59,"end":68,"text":"具有肿瘤病变的鸡病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"心肌","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"肝脏","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (三)剖检变化：本病不具有肉眼可见的病理变化，有时能见到心肌、肝脏切面上出现不甚明显的白斑、不足以作为诊断依据。本病与具有肿瘤病变的鸡病鉴别见表4-1。

label: [{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"姑息疗法","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":21,"text":"对病雏加强护理","labels":["control"]},{"start":22,"end":30,"text":"创造优起环境条件","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"病雏","labels":["type"]}]
text: 本病无药可治，只可姑息疗法，对病雏加强护理，创造优起环境条件，顺其目然，多数可以恢复，继续生长发育。

label: [{"start":12,"end":21,"text":"更新鸡群或淘汰病鸡","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"全场彻底毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":28,"end":42,"text":"不再从有病种鸡场进种蛋和雏鸡","labels":["control"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 为了防止本病的延续，最好更新鸡群或淘汰病鸡，全场彻底毒，不再从有病种鸡场进种蛋和雏鸡。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":20,"text":"执行严格的尊医卫生防疼制度","labels":["control"]},{"start":21,"end":26,"text":"杆绝水平传","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":33,"text":"确保鸡群健康","labels":["control"]},{"start":39,"end":48,"text":"进行本病的免疫接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"种鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 加强饲养管理，执行严格的尊医卫生防疼制度，杆绝水平传,确保鸡群健康。种鸡视情况进行本病的免疫接种，保护鸡群，提供优质种蛋和雏鸡。
